      <div style="break-inside: avoid; padding: 6px 0;">✓ <strong style="color: var(--navy); font-weight: 500;">Gmail Workspace, Outlook 365, Yahoo Mail</strong><br><span style="color: var(--ink-muted); font-style: italic; font-size: 0.88rem;">messageries grand public américaines</span></div>
